1999-11-11  Sung-Hyun Nam  <namsh@kldp.org>

	* src/pcScript.c (ScriptAutoRes): sync to new auto-response code
	(ScriptRemoveBookmark,ScriptRunButton): added g_list_remove call.
	* src/pcMain.h: auto response 관련 함수 prototype removed/modified
	* src/pcSetting.h (PC_AUTORES_FILE): definition removed.
